---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Container } from "@/components/layout/Container";
import HeroImage from "../components/ui/HeroImage.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Starting a Daycare | Childcare Business Plan"
    description="Your daycare business starts with understanding what makes your market unique. Get personalized insights based on your state's regulations and market conditions."
>
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="pt-8 pb-12 md:pt-12 md:pb-20">
        <Container size="md">
            <HeroImage
                src="/images/startup/starting-a-daycare.webp"
                alt="Modern daycare facility interior illustrating the successful result of following the steps to opening a childcare center"
                className="mb-8 md:mb-12"
            />
            <div class="text-center mb-8 md:mb-12">
                <span
                    class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-teal-100 text-teal-700 text-xs font-semibold mb-3"
                >
                    Getting Started
                </span>
                <h1
                    class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6"
                >
                    YOUR Daycare Business
                </h1>
                <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Starting a daycare isn't a one-size-fits-all journey. Your
                    state, your capacity, and your market create a unique
                    opportunity that generic advice can't capture.
                </p>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- FACTORS SECTION -->
    <section class="py-8 md:py-16">
        <Container size="md">
            <div
                class="glass-panel rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-10 mb-6 md:mb-8"
            >
                <h2
                    class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6"
                >
                    What Affects Your Success
                </h2>
                <div
                    class="space-y-4 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    <p>
                        Every daycare operates under different conditions that
                        dramatically impact both startup costs and income
                        potential. Your state's licensing requirements might
                        allow you to care for 6 children or 12. Your local
                        regulations might require extensive renovations or
                        minimal changes.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        These variables aren't just details—they're the
                        foundation of your business model. A home daycare in
                        Vermont operates under completely different constraints
                        than a center in Texas. The path that works for one
                        won't work for the other.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Beyond regulations, your local competition, demographic
                        composition, and even zoning laws create opportunities
                        and limitations unique to your situation.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- WHY GENERIC FAILS SECTION -->
    <section class="py-8 md:py-16">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="glass-panel rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-10">
                <h2
                    class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6"
                >
                    Why Online Advice Often Conflicts
                </h2>
                <div
                    class="space-y-4 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    <p>
                        You've probably noticed that every article about
                        starting a daycare tells a different story. One says you
                        need $50,000 to start, another says $5,000. One
                        recommends starting small from home, another insists you
                        need a commercial space from day one.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        They're both right—for someone. The problem is that
                        generic advice assumes conditions that might be
                        completely different from yours. What works in one
                        regulatory environment becomes impossible in another.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        This is why personalization isn't a luxury—it's a
                        necessity. You need to see the numbers for your state,
                        your capacity, and your market before you can make
                        confident decisions.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA SECTION -->
    <section class="py-12 md:py-20">
        <Container size="md">
            <div
                class="glass-panel rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-10 text-center border-2 border-teal-200/50 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50/50 to-white/50"
            >
                <h2
                    class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 md:mb-4"
                >
                    See How Much YOU Could Make in Your State
                </h2>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 mb-4 md:mb-6">
                    Get your personalized income estimate based on your state's
                    regulations and your business model.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="/#calculator"
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-medium px-6 py-3 md:px-8 md:py-4 shadow-lg transition-all text-sm md:text-base"
                >
                    Use the Free Calculator →
                </a>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>
</Layout>
